{"tid":804723,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"唉.......今日開學比人串到喊T︿T””","createTime":"2018-09-03T08:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T12:08:33.000Z","uid":52073,"like":21,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"038e4154e332795816ffdbf5f705d8295d4423b5","tid":804723,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:38:43.000Z","msg":"今日見d同學成班圍埋一齊講野,我想搭下嗲,點知佢地話我講野1999=.=<br />\n我話:你班傻的嗎仔緊係聽唔明我講乜啦,我智商600,所以你地同我溝通唔到姐?<br />\n然後其中一個同學聽到之後話: 哦...原來我地智商差成400咁多,唔怪之得啦...<br />\n咁我又接住講: 算啦,我都唔介意既...<br />\n點知佢地竟然話我弱智仔 仲同我講:我地呢度每個人既智商都係1000以上,又叫我死開啦,白痴仔..咁＝︿＝?<br />\n聽到佢地咁講我忍唔住流左少少眼淚,然後跑走左,不過當時我仲係好型棍&gt;3&lt;,?<br />\n果陣既我既嬲又唔開心 我決定唔讀小一啦,以後日日上連登hi 你地"},{"pid":"4388c46401e255bb0736ae79a19d1a5370237e62","tid":804723,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"橙橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc56328aef0d2606db6c1c41e72018196688dcd","tid":804723,"uid":147871,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/164111_93bf296868f2c690fda4620986c40d3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F164111_93bf296868f2c690fda4620986c40d3e.png&h=63174ecf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"401cfd7984e4c14dbc06dbdd42f11067cb93b97d","tid":804723,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"kpop狗"},{"pid":"ef8bf33aced2339ae2deaa310179230ce82f6c59","tid":804723,"uid":52073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"樓上班人成日針對小妹-,-"},{"pid":"1705b3dfa72cbc4806e8150b8213e2a3e9faa011","tid":804723,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"弱智仔"},{"pid":"f430ea9b049ea367b5e8b8989eb6135893ece95f","tid":804723,"uid":187076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":