色口罩關係<br />\n一番到學己經有幾個女同學借d意埋身問我邊到買嫁又抽下我水咁<br />\n點估到佢地狼到話放學一齊番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家門口有4條女等緊我放學點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我遲番屋企會比媽咪鬧死<br />\n唔通我生得型都係錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4505acf342806c27acba7ab95b601536b1e57b8","tid":804723,"uid":52073,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5fd5c87ceebf56902cd08ad0b0e54ff90463fb90","tid":804723,"uid":204852,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:55:17.000Z","msg":"弱撚智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:01:26.000Z","msg":"知吾知自己好撚戇尻？<br />\n我都忍左你好撚耐<br />\n日日扮撚哂大家姐<br />\n認真講 係F.1女仔最壞係我同凱婷<br />\n你要扮我地吾會阻止<br />\n哈 點知你越扮越衰<br />\n有啲野我同凱婷都未出聲<br />\n有時連班男既都未出聲啦<br />\n幾時輪到你出聲呀？<br />\n有啲野心照架<br />\n壞學生？你做到咩？<br />\n吸煙飲酒介手就代表壞囉<br />\n你連扣分 係學校搞事都吾敢啦<br />\n點做壞學生呀？ 小姐<br />\n你想學我地咋嘛<br />\n入黑社囉 係學校搞事呀！<br />\n最好學理我負分都要比人繼續扣<br />\n你敢？你連續兩支煙都食吾*到啦<br />\n學我地？！算把啦 傻系"},{"pid":"c703ceda95d6595b786cbebaccb306a987be0f87","tid":804723,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:09:55.000Z","msg":"叫動物台手足同佢地做忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6585f621b4c74cec4a634a4a4b928cffbefaa407","tid":804723,"uid":78643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"叫wendy教訓佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a221d868dbedb38feff8bc16f84a224c781618e","tid":804723,"uid":151675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"憨鳩冇撚得救<img src